  "text": "Amazon Echo Show 15 Amazon Echo Show 15 You can't go wrong with a large smart display. Not only does it provide information at a glance, but you can also use it as a media hub. Right now, the Echo Show 15 is down to $180. There are a lot of great smart displays on the market, but if you're looking for one that has a large screen that's great for families, the Echo Show 15 is going to be it. While ther current version is pretty pricey, coming in at $300, we've found a good deal on the previous model that comes in at just $180. Related What's great about the Amazon Echo Show 15? The Echo Show 15 was a fine device when it first launched and still continues to be an essential for anyone looking for a large smart display in 2025. As far as some of the things we love about this device, it's going to be all about the large 15-inch screen. With this much screen real estate, you're getting a huge canvas to work with, which is great if you're someone that likes to get a ton of information at a glance. The design is fairly reserved too, which means this smart display doesn't look out of place, no matter where you put it in your home. It's also quite versatile as well, and can be used in both landscape and portrait orientations. Furthermore, the software also provides a wealth of features, allowing you to get the information you need quickly through widgets, or you can even listen to and watch your favorite streaming media as well. If you have other compatible smart home devices, they can also be controlled and monitored through the Echo Show 15. For the most part, this really is a great smart display, and we did like a lot of things about it. While there is a newer model, we think that this one offers great value, especially at its current price of $180.",
