u003eThere are a lot of \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-smart-displays/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003egreat smart displays on the market\u003c/a\u003e, but if you\u0026#39;re looking for one that has a large screen that\u0026#39;s great for families, the Echo Show 15 is going to be it. While ther current version is pretty pricey, coming in at $300, we\u0026#39;ve found a good deal on the previous model that comes in at just $180.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"734f-44d0-acfff7bdf7b3\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/amazon-echo-show-15-review/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2500\" height=\"1666\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"echo show 15 review hero 3\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/echo-show-15-review-hero-3.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-amazon-echo-show-15\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Amazon Echo Show 15?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Echo Show 15 was a fine device when it first launched and still continues to be an essential for anyone looking for a large smart display in 2025. As far as some of the things we love about this device, it\u0026#39;s going to be all about the large 15-inch screen.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWith this much screen real estate, you\u0026#39;re getting a huge canvas to work with, which is great if you\u0026#39;re someone that likes to get a ton of information at a glance. The design is fairly reserved too, which means this smart display doesn\u0026#39;t look out of place, no matter where you put it in your home.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s also quite versatile as well, and can be used in both landscape and portrait orientations. Furthermore, the software also provides a wealth of features, allowing you to get the information you need quickly through widgets, or you can even listen to and watch your favorite streaming media as well.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIf you have other compatible smart home devices, they can also be controlled and monitored through the Echo Show 15. For the most part, this really is a great smart display, and we did like a lot of things about it. While there is \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/amazon-echo-show-15-2nd-gen-review/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea newer model\u003c/a\u003e, we think that this one offers great value, especially at its current price of $180.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
